{"tid":629223,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"金管局買港元點解會令銀行結餘少左？","createTime":"2018-04-14T13:44:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T03:36:54.000Z","uid":42977,"like":12,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"43532737ba9a3c69c3afce2611ca90fed92d1f45","tid":629223,"uid":42977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T13:44:08.000Z","msg":"睇左幾個 post 同 文章<br />\n<br />\n仲係唔明HKMA 用USD 跟銀行買多到無人要既港幤，點樣令到喺香港既錢少左&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n假設有HKD 78,500多左<br />\nHKMA 用 USD10,000買<br />\n呢個交同我喺銀行唱美金有乜分別？個市場／香港仲係有價值 USD 10,000 or HKD78,500 喺到架<br />\n你話流出香港我就明，個HKMA 唱錢又有乜大影響？<br />\n求高手解答"},{"pid":"88d01c05bad2eebad4fd48da352634afb7854748","tid":629223,"uid":85659,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T13:48:47.000Z","msg":"銀行有得渣1美印7.8hkd"},{"pid":"e71f9ff06bd0ef966438bbc21e6f7d7087e0f365","tid":629223,"uid":3302,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T13:56:31.000Z","msg":"金管局係銀行體系入面抽走游資接沽盤<br />\n拆息抽高"},{"pid":"1f63d676e5dab7a3ca7a37147c1b36ac5701ae28","tid":629223,"uid":160084,"like":71,"dislike":1,"score":70,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T14:02:21.000Z","msg":"買入港元簡單黎講係用外幣向銀行買，之後收埋佢。所以銀行既港元會少左。<br />\n<br />\n因為港元弱，買入港元可以增加向港元既需求（或抽走銀行既港元，令供應下跌），最終港元會升值。"},{"pid":"25113925bf25737b269319a9fffa048eecceede2","tid":629223,"uid":55614,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T14:03:10.000Z","msg":"分清楚邊個係莊家未"},{"pid":"c5546c2d4a8790a72d774629b6a6be0e64de7cec","tid":629223,"uid":42977,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"88d01c05bad2eebad4fd48da352634afb7854748","tid":629223,"uid":85659,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T13:48:47.000Z","msg":"銀行有得渣1美印7.8hkd"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T14:03:41.000Z","msg":"即係香港體系多左USD1 入黎，本港銀行就除時可以印多HKD7.8?"},{"pid":"b53836cccfc1c021e33f3228f8187efa9232b599","tid":629223,"uid":42977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f63d676e5dab7a3ca7a37147c1b36ac5701ae28","t